SELECT COALESCE("t2"."POSTID", "t2"."POSTID") AS "POSTID", "t2"."TITLE", "t2"."CREATIONDATE", "t2"."VIEWCOUNT", "t2"."SCORE", "t2"."ANSWERCOUNT", "t2"."COMMENTCOUNT", "t2"."UPVOTES", "t2"."DOWNVOTES", "t2"."OWNERDISPLAYNAME", "t4"."POSTID" AS "POSTID0", "t4"."CLOSECOUNT", "t4"."REOPENCOUNT"
FROM (SELECT ANY_VALUE("t"."Id") AS "POSTID", "t"."Title" AS "TITLE", "t"."CreationDate" AS "CREATIONDATE", "t"."ViewCount" AS "VIEWCOUNT", "t"."Score" AS "SCORE", "t"."AnswerCount" AS "ANSWERCOUNT", COUNT(CASE WHEN "Comments"."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "COMMENTCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("t"."VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "UPVOTES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("t"."VoteTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "DOWNVOTES", ANY_VALUE("t"."DisplayName") AS "OWNERDISPLAYNAME"
FROM (SELECT "Posts"."Id", "Posts"."PostTypeId", "Posts"."AcceptedAnswerId", "Posts"."ParentId", "Posts"."CreationDate", "Posts"."Score", "Posts"."ViewCount", "Posts"."Body", "Posts"."OwnerUserId", "Posts"."OwnerDisplayName", "Posts"."LastEditorUserId", "Posts"."LastEditorDisplayName", "Posts"."LastEditDate", "Posts"."LastActivityDate", "Posts"."Title", "Posts"."Tags", "Posts"."AnswerCount", "Posts"."CommentCount", "Posts"."FavoriteCount", "Posts"."ClosedDate", "Posts"."CommunityOwnedDate", "Posts"."ContentLicense", "Users"."Id" AS "Id0", "Users"."Reputation", "Users"."CreationDate" AS "CreationDate0", "Users"."DisplayName", "Users"."LastAccessDate", "Users"."WebsiteUrl", "Users"."Location", "Users"."AboutMe", "Users"."Views", "Users"."UpVotes", "Users"."DownVotes", "Users"."ProfileImageUrl", "Users"."AccountId", "Votes"."Id" AS "Id1", "Votes"."PostId", "Votes"."VoteTypeId", "Votes"."UserId", "Votes"."CreationDate" AS "CreationDate1", "Votes"."BountyAmount"
FROM "STACK"."Votes"
RIGHT JOIN ("STACK"."Posts" LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Users" ON "Posts"."OwnerUserId" = "Users"."Id") ON "Votes"."PostId" = "Posts"."Id") AS "t"
LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Comments" ON "t"."Id" = "Comments"."PostId"
GROUP BY "t"."Id", "t"."Title", "t"."CreationDate", "t"."ViewCount", "t"."Score", "t"."AnswerCount", "t"."DisplayName") AS "t2"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "PostId" AS "POSTID", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostHistoryTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 10 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "CLOSECOUNT", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostHistoryTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 11 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "REOPENCOUNT"
FROM "STACK"."PostHistory"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t4" ON "t2"."POSTID" = "t4"."POSTID"